    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Up for sale is a solid, well-maintained vehicle in good overall condition. The exterior looks great with a healthy shine, though closer inspection reveals minor stone chips on the hood and a few light scratches on the rear bumper from normal use. Mechanically, it is very reliable; the engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts as expected without any hesitation. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, showing only light wear on the driver\u2019s seat bolster and a few scuffs on the door panels. This car is ready for its next owner and provides a dependable driving experience without needing immediate repairs.",
