    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid project or budget-friendly driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable paint fading on the roof and hood, along with a few minor dents and scratches around the body. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and visible wear on the driver's seat, though all major electronics remain functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely need a suspension refresh and a tune-up in the near future to ensure long-term reliability.",
