      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in truly pristine condition. This motorcar represents the pinnacle of its class, offering an uncompromising blend of mechanical excellence and aesthetic perfection. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the meticulously preserved interior, reflects a standard of care rarely encountered on the secondary market. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than showroom quality, this offering stands as a definitive benchmark of automotive integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
